data.description: Here's a perk: purchase this home and you may qualify for an Assumable, FHA Loan at 5.37%! This Beazer, "Chadwick" floor plan is a rare, like-new (1-year old) home priced under $700K in Nolensville. The Lochridge neighborhood recently sold out of its new construction inventory. Families have enjoyed moving here for the convenient location, community pool, playground, walking trail, and access to Williamson County Schools. This home is immaculately presented, features an upgraded kitchen appliance package with double-oven, 8 foot granite island, and walk-in pantry. The Great Room is bright and comfy, and a sliding glass door walks out to your covered patio. The upstairs bonus room offers almost 400sf of space for family recreation. This home is also built with several energy efficient features, including tankless water heater - your utility bills will be kept in check. Don't miss out on this one!
